If you have an ssd for your OS and a harddisk for your data.

You should put this file as root in the following directory.

/etc/polkit-1/rules.d/49-nopasswd_global.rules

Source : 

https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Polkit#Example

if you are not owner of this new harddrive

sudo chown erik /mnt/DATA

I name it always DATA so I do not have to change my scripts